ul.li:
                        ToolWindowType.DOCKED
                        - When DOCKED type is used, the tool window shares frame space and fixes to a docking
                        area along one of the tool window bars (the one containing the corresponding representative button).



                            To set ToolWindowType.DOCKED type use the following:
                            
                                ToolWindow toolWindow = toolWindowManager.getToolWindow("Debug Tool");
                                toolWindow.setType(ToolWindowType.DOCKED);
